 WACTOR Production (910inc) 3名VTuber指责公司不公平对待，有些甚至试图结束自己的生命https://p2y.jp/wactor-product-910inc-vtuber-accused-of-unfair-treatment-by-the-company/ https://p2y.jp/wactor-product-910inc-vtuber-accused-of-unfair-treatment-by-the-company/#respondp2y_admin Sun, 18 Feb 2024 05:16:50 +0000 VTuberバーチャル910incTwitterWACTORプロダクションYouTuberネムリメチャロバーチャルYouTuberヒメラギアゲハ天上ユイガ https://p2y.jp/?p=116064 <p> VTuber Nemuri Mecharo（所属：WACTOR Production (910inc)/管理：WACTOR Co., Ltd.）、Himeragiageha（同上）和 Tenjo Yuiga（同上）将于 2024 年 […]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/wactor-production-910inc-vtuber-accused-of-unfair-treatment-by-the-company/">WACTOR Production (910inc) 3 VTuber 指责该公司不公平对待，而试图自杀的人</a>首先出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p> VTuber <strong>Nemuri Mecharo</strong> （所属： <strong>WACTOR Production</strong> (910inc) / 管理： <strong>WACTOR Co., Ltd.</strong> ）、 <strong>Himagiageha</strong> （上同）、 <strong>Tenjo Yuiga</strong> （上同）由公司于 2024 年 2 月 18 日公布（Reiwa） 6).被指控不公平待遇。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1200" height="676" data-attachment-id="116081" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/wactor-production-910inc-vtuber-accused-of-unfair-treatment-by-the-company/wactor_production_910inc_vtuber_accused_of_unfair_treatment_by_the_company/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/wactor_production_910inc_vtuber_accused_of_unfair_treatment_by_the_company.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,676" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="wactor_production_910inc_vtuber_accused_of_unfair_treatment_by_the_company" data